snippet.title: The Swoop 64 - Homebrew N64 game
snippet.description: The Swoop 64 is a homebrew game for the N64 by Zestydavy and Miluaces where you steal things from around the neighbourhood to build up your nest.. Get the ROM and find out more: https://n64squid.com/the-swoop-64/
